    <item>
      <title>Re: NewsletterNodeID and override for template</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/nvnewsletter/forum/general/newsletternodeid_and_override_for_template/re_newsletternodeid_and_override_for_template2</link>
      <description>Newsletter uses node/view/nvnewsletterhtml.tpl and node/view/nvnewslettertext.tpl templates by default. If you want to create your own templates you can override these default templates with following settings.&#13;
&#13;
&lt;code&gt;&#13;
[my_newsletter_html]&#13;
Source=node/view/nvnewsletterhtml.tpl&#13;
MatchFile=newsletter/my_newsletter_html.tpl&#13;
Subdir=templates&#13;
Match[class_identifier]=my_newsletter&#13;
&#13;
[my_newsletter_text]&#13;
Source=node/view/nvnewslettertext.tpl&#13;
MatchFile=newsletter/my_newsletter_text.tpl&#13;
Subdir=templates&#13;
Match[class_identifier]=my_newsletter&#13;
&lt;/code&gt;</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Tero Auralinna)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/nvnewsletter/forum/general/newsletternodeid_and_override_for_template/re_newsletternodeid_and_override_for_template2</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Aug 2010 16:18:53 +0000</pubDate>
    </item>
